FuncDef: This command is used to specify the type of the traffic descriptor profile as per ATM Forum Traffic Management Specification Version 4.1.

ParaDef.Info: defines interpretation of traffic parameters that are specified for this profile. Values-P0_1, P0_1andS0_Tag, P0_1andS0, P0_1andS0_1.

ExtraInfo:
